div.p:
Committee IV, which was the only Committee which had not so far completed its
                    work, met this morning and approved fourteen resolutions with titles as follows:


Sale and distribution of primary products; Industrial development;
                            Inter-American transportation; Economic charter of the Americas;
                            Processing of primary products; Methods of preventing unemployment; Work
                            of the Inter-American Development Commission; Health and sanitation;
                            Social questions; Charter for women and children; Inter-American
                            cooperation in the care of European children; Declaration of social
                            principles of the Americas; Proclaimed Lists; and, Meeting of central
                            banks or similar institutions.
